title: Episode 349: Pregnant Sex is the Best Sex (Feat. Mooski & Onika McLean)
itunes:title: Episode 349: Pregnant Sex is the Best Sex (Feat. Mooski & Onika McLean)
description:
Rapper, Mooski joins the ladies of Lip Service to promote his debut album "Melodic Therapy 4 The Broken" alongside Comdian, Onika McLean. Mooski speaks on his growth now that his girlfriend will be having their first son in the coming weeks. The group discuss the process of having a home-birth, the amazingness of pregnant sex, and much more. Onika even opens about the first and last time she tried S&M...enjoy!
